@startuml
title StateSpec Compiler And Generation Pipeline

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

rectangle ".sspec text" as Text
rectangle "Lexer" as Lexer
rectangle "Parser" as Parser
rectangle "AST" as AST
rectangle "Semantic validator" as Validator
rectangle "Symbol table" as Symbols
rectangle "Canonical IR" as IR

rectangle "Formatter" as Formatter
rectangle "CLI" as CLI
rectangle "LSP / IDE tools" as LSP
rectangle "Generators" as Generators

rectangle "C++ bindings" as Cpp
rectangle "Go bindings" as Go
rectangle "Java bindings" as Java
rectangle "Rust bindings" as Rust
rectangle "OpenAPI / protobuf / diagrams / tests" as Other

Text --> Lexer
Lexer --> Parser
Parser --> AST
AST --> Validator
Validator --> Symbols
Validator --> IR

Lexer --> Formatter
AST --> CLI
IR --> CLI
IR --> LSP
IR --> Generators

Generators --> Cpp
Generators --> Go
Generators --> Java
Generators --> Rust
Generators --> Other

note right of Text
Text is the source of truth.
Visual tools and generated artifacts
must derive from .sspec files.
end note

note right of IR
Generators consume canonical IR,
not raw AST or raw text.
end note

@enduml
